# 🎨 Brand Design System & Color Palette Guideline

> Reverse-engineered from **Nickel** — a fintech/payments SaaS homepage

---

## 1. Brand Identity

| Attribute | Value |
|---|---|
| **Brand Name** | Nickel |
| **Industry** | Fintech / B2B Payments |
| **Tone** | Professional yet playful, approachable, modern |
| **Personality** | Confident, innovative, human-friendly |
| **Logo Style** | Geometric circle mark + clean lowercase wordmark |

### Logo Specifications
- **Mark**: Solid orange filled circle (acts as the "O" brand element)
- **Wordmark**: Lowercase sans-serif "nickel" — clean, geometric letterforms
- **Logo Color**: Primary Orange `#E8611A` on white background
- **Minimum Clear Space**: Equal to the height of the circle mark on all sides

---

## 2. Color Palette

### Primary Colors

| Swatch | Name | Hex | RGB | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 🟠 | **Primary Orange** | `#E8611A` | `rgb(232, 97, 26)` | Logo, brand accents, icon highlights |
| 🔴 | **Accent Coral-Red** | `#E94E35` | `rgb(233, 78, 53)` | Primary CTA buttons, hover states |
| ⬛ | **Rich Black** | `#1A1A1A` | `rgb(26, 26, 26)` | Headlines, primary text |

### Neutral Colors

| Swatch | Name | Hex | RGB | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| ⬜ | **Pure White** | `#FFFFFF` | `rgb(255, 255, 255)` | Page background, card backgrounds |
| 🔘 | **Warm Gray BG** | `#F5F3F0` | `rgb(245, 243, 240)` | Section backgrounds, subtle separation |
| 🔘 | **Light Gray** | `#E8E5E1` | `rgb(232, 229, 225)` | Borders, dividers, subtle UI elements |
| 🔘 | **Medium Gray** | `#6B6B6B` | `rgb(107, 107, 107)` | Body text, secondary text |
| 🔘 | **Dark Gray** | `#333333` | `rgb(51, 51, 51)` | Navigation text, sub-headings |

### 3D Illustration Palette (Extended)

| Swatch | Name | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| 🟡 | **Matte Yellow-Orange** | `#F2922B` | 3D model body, warm surfaces |
| 🟠 | **Deep Orange** | `#D4561A` | 3D shadows, depth areas |
| 🔴 | **Glossy Red** | `#CC3326` | 3D accent parts (buttons, phone receiver) |
| ⚪ | **Warm Cream** | `#F0E8DD` | 3D keyboard keys, light plastic surfaces |
| ⬛ | **Screen Dark** | `#2B2B2B` | CRT screen background, terminal display |
| 🟢 | **Terminal Green** | `#7FCC7F` | Terminal text on screens |

### Gradient Usage
- **Hero Background**: Subtle warm-to-neutral gradient — `#FFFFFF` → `#F5F3F0` (top to bottom)
- **CTA Hover**: `#E94E35` → `#D43E28` (darken 10% on hover)
- **No heavy gradients** — the brand aesthetic is flat and clean

---

## 3. Typography

### Font Stack

| Role | Font Family | Fallback | Weight | Style |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Headings** | `"Inter"` or `"Outfit"` | `system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif` | 700 (Bold) | Normal |
| **Body** | `"Inter"` | `system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif` | 400 (Regular) | Normal |
| **Navigation** | `"Inter"` | `system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif` | 500 (Medium) | Normal |
| **Buttons** | `"Inter"` | `system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif` | 600 (Semi-bold) | Normal |

### Type Scale

| Element | Size | Line Height | Letter Spacing | Weight | Color |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **H1 (Hero)** | `56px` / `3.5rem` | `1.1` | `-0.02em` | 700 | `#1A1A1A` |
| **H2 (Section)** | `40px` / `2.5rem` | `1.15` | `-0.01em` | 700 | `#1A1A1A` |
| **H3 (Sub-section)** | `28px` / `1.75rem` | `1.2` | `0` | 600 | `#1A1A1A` |
| **Body Large** | `18px` / `1.125rem` | `1.6` | `0` | 400 | `#6B6B6B` |
| **Body Regular** | `16px` / `1rem` | `1.5` | `0` | 400 | `#6B6B6B` |
| **Nav Links** | `15px` / `0.9375rem` | `1` | `0` | 500 | `#333333` |
| **Button Text** | `15px` / `0.9375rem` | `1` | `0.01em` | 600 | `#FFFFFF` / `#333333` |
| **Caption** | `13px` / `0.8125rem` | `1.4` | `0.02em` | 400 | `#6B6B6B` |

### Key Typography Rules
- Hero headline uses **short, punchy sentences** with line breaks for visual rhythm
- Body copy under hero is kept to **2 lines maximum** — concise and scannable
- **No ALL-CAPS** in primary UI (exception: very small labels/badges)
- Heading text is always **Rich Black** `#1A1A1A`, never pure `#000000`

---

## 4. Spacing & Layout

### Spacing Scale (8px Base Unit)

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `--space-xs` | `4px` | Tight inline spacing |
| `--space-sm` | `8px` | Icon gaps, tight padding |
| `--space-md` | `16px` | Component internal padding |
| `--space-lg` | `24px` | Section padding, card padding |
| `--space-xl` | `32px` | Between components |
| `--space-2xl` | `48px` | Between sections |
| `--space-3xl` | `64px` | Major section margins |
| `--space-4xl` | `96px` | Hero vertical padding |
| `--space-5xl` | `128px` | Page-level spacing |

### Layout Grid
- **Container Max Width**: `1200px`
- **Side Padding**: `24px` (mobile) / `48px` (tablet) / `64px` (desktop)
- **Hero Layout**: 2-column asymmetric — **55% text / 45% illustration**
- **Navigation Height**: `72px`
- **Grid System**: 12-column with `24px` gutters

### Content Alignment
- Text content is **left-aligned** (no centered hero text)
- CTA buttons are **left-aligned** under the hero copy
- Navigation is **justified** — logo left, links center, CTA right

---

## 5. Component Styles

### Buttons

#### Primary CTA Button
```css
.btn-primary {
  background-color: #E94E35;
  color: #FFFFFF;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 15px;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
}
.btn-primary:hover {
  background-color: #D43E28;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}
```

#### Secondary Button (Ghost/Outline)
```css
.btn-secondary {
  background-color: transparent;
  color: #333333;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 15px;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1.5px solid #E8E5E1;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
}
.btn-secondary:hover {
  border-color: #333333;
  background-color: #F5F3F0;
}
```

#### Navigation CTA (Small)
```css
.btn-nav-cta {
  background-color: #E94E35;
  color: #FFFFFF;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 14px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  border: none;
}
```

### Navigation Bar
```css
.navbar {
  height: 72px;
  background: #FFFFFF;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #F5F3F0;
  padding: 0 48px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
}
```

### Cards
```css
.card {
  background: #FFFFFF;
  border: 1px solid #E8E5E1;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 32px;
  transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
}
.card:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}
```

---

## 6. 3D Illustration Art Direction

### Style Definition
| Attribute | Description |
|---|---|
| **Render Style** | Matte / semi-glossy 3D with soft shadows |
| **Aesthetic** | Retro-futuristic — vintage CRT computers, rotary phones, and tech objects reimagined in vibrant modern colors |
| **Color Treatment** | Monochromatic orange with red and cream accents |
| **Lighting** | Soft, diffused studio lighting from upper-left — no harsh shadows |
| **Background** | Always on clean white/off-white — objects float without a ground plane |
| **Material Finish** | Matte plastic with subtle specularity on edges |
| **Playful Elements** | Smiley faces, stickers ("IGNORE"), cursor icons, terminal text |
| **Perspective** | Slightly elevated 3/4 view, gentle rotation |

### Art Direction Prompt (for 3D generation)
> "A retro-futuristic 3D robot made from a vintage CRT computer monitor and rotary phone parts. The robot is primarily matte orange and yellow-orange with red accent pieces. It has a dark screen displaying green terminal text. The body incorporates keyboard keys in warm cream color. Include playful details like stickers, a smiley face, and a cursor icon. Render with soft studio lighting on a clean white background. Semi-glossy matte plastic material. 3/4 perspective view."

---

## 7. Interaction & Animation Principles

| Effect | Duration | Easing | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Button Hover** | `200ms` | `ease` | Color shift + subtle lift (`translateY(-1px)`) |
| **Card Hover** | `300ms` | `ease` | Shadow expansion + lift (`translateY(-2px)`) |
| **Page Transitions** | `400ms` | `ease-in-out` | Fade + slide-up on scroll-reveal |
| **Nav Dropdown** | `200ms` | `ease-out` | Fade-in + slide-down |
| **Link Hover** | `150ms` | `ease` | Color shift to Primary Orange |
| **3D Element** | `continuous` | `ease-in-out` | Subtle floating animation (if animated) |

### Micro-interaction Guidelines
- Buttons should have **tactile feedback** — slight scale or lift on hover
- Links in nav should transition color smoothly to `#E8611A` on hover
- Dropdowns indicated by chevron `▾` that rotates `180°` on open
- Scroll-triggered animations use **fade-up** with `30px` offset

---

## 8. Iconography & Visual Elements

| Element | Style |
|---|---|
| **Icons** | Outlined or filled, 2px stroke, rounded joins |
| **Icon Size** | 20px (inline), 24px (nav), 48px (feature cards) |
| **Dropdown Indicator** | Small chevron `▾` — `10px`, `#6B6B6B` |
| **Dividers** | 1px solid `#E8E5E1` — used sparingly |
| **Badges** | Small rounded-pill, `#F5F3F0` background, `#333333` text |

---

## 9. Responsive Breakpoints

| Breakpoint | Width | Behavior |
|---|---|---|
| **Mobile** | `< 640px` | Single column, stacked hero, hamburger nav |
| **Tablet** | `640px – 1024px` | 2 columns, compact spacing |
| **Desktop** | `1024px – 1440px` | Full layout, 12-col grid |
| **Wide** | `> 1440px` | Max-width container centered, no stretch |

---

## 10. Do's and Don'ts

### ✅ Do
- Use generous whitespace — let elements breathe
- Keep CTAs visually prominent with the coral-red color
- Use the warm gray `#F5F3F0` for alternating section backgrounds
- Pair bold headlines with lightweight body copy for contrast
- Use 3D illustrations as hero focal points — they are the "wow" factor
- Left-align hero content for a professional, editorial feel

### ❌ Don't
- Don't use pure black `#000000` for text — always use `#1A1A1A`
- Don't center-align hero text — this brand is left-aligned editorial style
- Don't use gradients on buttons — flat color with hover transitions
- Don't overcrowd sections — this design thrives on minimalism
- Don't use more than 2 typefaces
- Don't place text over 3D illustrations — they occupy separate visual lanes

---

## 11. LLM Agent Prompt (Ready to Feed)

Copy the prompt below and feed it to your LLM agent to reproduce this design system:

---

```
You are building a modern fintech SaaS landing page. Follow this brand design system exactly:

**COLOR PALETTE:**
- Primary Orange: #E8611A (logo, accents, link hovers)
- CTA Coral-Red: #E94E35 (primary buttons, CTAs)
- Rich Black: #1A1A1A (headlines — never use pure #000)
- Medium Gray: #6B6B6B (body text, descriptions)
- Dark Gray: #333333 (nav text, sub-headings)
- Warm Gray Background: #F5F3F0 (alternate sections)
- Light Gray Border: #E8E5E1 (borders, dividers, outline buttons)
- White: #FFFFFF (primary background, cards)

**TYPOGRAPHY:**
- Font: "Inter" from Google Fonts (fallback: system-ui, sans-serif)
- H1: 56px, bold (700), line-height 1.1, letter-spacing -0.02em, color #1A1A1A
- H2: 40px, bold (700), line-height 1.15
- Body: 18px, regular (400), line-height 1.6, color #6B6B6B
- Nav: 15px, medium (500), color #333333
- Buttons: 15px, semi-bold (600)

**LAYOUT:**
- Max container width: 1200px, centered
- Hero section: 2-column asymmetric layout (55% text left, 45% visual right)
- Text is LEFT-ALIGNED, not centered
- Generous whitespace between sections (64-96px)
- Navigation: sticky, 72px height, glassmorphism (backdrop-blur + semi-transparent white)

**BUTTONS:**
- Primary: #E94E35 background, white text, 8px border-radius, 14px 28px padding
- Secondary: transparent background, #333333 text, 1.5px #E8E5E1 border, 8px border-radius
- Hover: darken primary to #D43E28, subtle translateY(-1px) lift
- Nav CTA: smaller version of primary button

**COMPONENTS:**
- Cards: white background, 1px #E8E5E1 border, 12px border-radius, hover shadow + lift
- Navigation: logo left, links with dropdowns in center, login + CTA right
- Dropdown indicators: small chevrons that rotate on open

**ANIMATIONS:**
- All transitions: 200-300ms ease
- Buttons: color + subtle lift on hover
- Cards: shadow expansion + 2px lift on hover
- Scroll: fade-up reveal with 30px offset
- Links: smooth color transition to #E8611A on hover

**DESIGN PRINCIPLES:**
- Clean, minimal, lots of whitespace
- Professional but playful (the 3D illustrations add personality)
- Warm neutral tones — never cold blues or grays
- Editorial left-aligned typography, not centered
- Section backgrounds alternate between #FFFFFF and #F5F3F0
- Flat design for UI elements — no gradients on buttons
```

